race.comment: The very well-related TIME OF MY LIFE (10) (half to 25xG1 winner Winx) has been right there in both starts since joining the Gollan barn and looks to be building up to another victory. Ready to peak third-up and looks the one they all have to run down. CASINO BAY (13) hasn't done much wrong with a win and a second from two starts to date and has revved up for this with two recent trials. Plenty of upside and can measure up. DIVINE SOURCE (7) resumes here but the form she showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this nature. Include in calculations. MR BUBBALUSKI (2) has placed four from four around this circuit and is a must for the multiples. TOPHET (4) is a former Victorian having his first run for the new stable and any market support should be respected.
